readings.question: Trying the tooltips again for Five Card spread...
readings.cardTooltip2:
Power, command, authority, militant 
            intelligence, law, offices 
            of the crown, and so forth.
readings.cardTooltip3:
In the main, it is a card of money, 
            business, barter — but it can also mean 
            quarrel, innocence, ingenuity, purgation.

readings.cardTooltip3:
